No.

00:18:50.230 --> 00:18:51.560
The coat is warm.

00:19:04.120 --> 00:19:05.160
You are really not cold?

00:19:05.470 --> 00:19:06.920
Of course, it's cold! I'm freezing to death.

00:19:07.030 --> 00:19:08.290
So why you don't join me.

