Whatever. What can we do?

00:19:14.520 --> 00:19:16.000
We can't sit here for whole night.

00:19:18.950 --> 00:19:20.010
We don't have any choice,

00:19:20.950 --> 00:19:22.160
but stay here tonight.

00:19:24.190 --> 00:19:25.120
You really don't want it?

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:32.680
See the moon.

00:19:33.890 --> 00:19:36.160
It's a full moon. Like egg custard.

00:19:37.590 --> 00:19:38.800
You must be hungry.

00:19:40.210 --> 00:19:42.900
My mom used to cook delicious egg custard for me when I was a child.

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:46.830
I've never eaten such

00:19:49.590 --> 00:19:50.400
delicious egg custard

00:19:50.400 --> 00:19:51.470
since she passed away.

00:19:55.540 --> 00:19:56.900
Close your eyes and have a sleep.

00:19:57.840 --> 00:19:59.380
You won't feel hungry while you are asleep.

00:20:31.430 --> 00:20:32.590
Officer Zheng.

00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:38.110
You are so diligent.

00:20:38.110 --> 00:20:39.640
Practicing your Kungfu this early?

00:20:39.640 --> 00:20:40.800
Young blood.

00:20:40.800 --> 00:20:41.400
Where's Magistrate Tang?

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:42.680
Magistrate Tang?

00:20:43.430 --> 00:20:45.640
Didn't he go to autopsy room last night?

00:20:45.640 --> 00:20:46.680
Autopsy?

00:20:48.350 --> 00:20:49.070
Where's Tang?

00:20:51.070 --> 00:20:53.520
Isn't he in his room?

00:20:54.110 --> 00:20:55.000
Nope.

00:20:56.760 --> 00:20:58.800
Where did he go?

00:20:59.310 --> 00:21:03.710
Bow to each other. You are husband and wife now.

00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:07.590
Wait. What is this situation?

00:21:08.430 --> 00:21:11.400
Honey, it's me.

00:21:11.400 --> 00:21:14.760
Zhu Dacong? Why are you here?

00:21:15.920 --> 00:21:18.590
Honey, it's our big day.

00:21:18.590 --> 00:21:20.190
From now on, you are my wife.

00:21:20.760 --> 00:21:22.400
I am your husband.

00:21:22.400 --> 00:21:25.470
Bullshit! I won't marry you.

00:21:25.470 --> 00:21:27.710
Honey, even the ceremony is over.

00:21:27.710 --> 00:21:29.590
Now we should take the next step.

00:21:30.430 --> 00:21:32.430
Go away. I won't marry you.

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:35.040
Why does my hand hurt so bad?

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:36.590
What do you think?

00:21:37.310 --> 00:21:38.640
Why are you covering your face?

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:39.680
What do you think?

00:21:42.190 --> 00:21:43.760
Is it because of me?

00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:44.710
What do you think?

00:21:46.070 --> 00:21:46.710
I'm having tinnitus.

00:21:47.880 --> 00:21:49.280
I had a dream.

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.110
Who is so blind

00:21:53.110 --> 00:21:54.110
that he wants to marry you?

00:21:54.560 --> 00:21:55.830
Doesn't he fear getting hit?

00:21:55.830 --> 00:21:57.680
A lot of men wanna marry me.

00:21:58.280 --> 00:21:59.560
If it's true,

00:21:59.560 --> 00:22:00.470
just pick a guy and marry him

00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:03.000
before he regrets it. Or it will be a pity.

00:22:04.430 --> 00:22:06.190
Pity for what?

00:22:06.190 --> 00:22:08.310
It's his fortune to marry me.

00:22:11.110 --> 00:22:12.340
Thank god, I don't have such fortune.

00:22:12.830 --> 00:22:13.470
Exactly!

00:22:15.470 --> 00:22:16.710
Thanks for not marrying me.

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:23.560
Someone's coming.

00:22:25.160 --> 00:22:26.590
My lord, why are you here?

00:22:26.590 --> 00:22:27.760
Everyone is looking for you!

00:22:28.310 --> 00:22:29.470
Hurry up.

00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:30.680
Let's go.

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:32.880
Your clothes.

00:22:37.190 --> 00:22:38.470
Slow down. My feet hurt.

00:22:46.710 --> 00:22:48.070
Enough. Don't cry.

00:22:48.350 --> 00:22:49.430
It's no use to cry.

00:22:49.430 --> 00:22:50.280
It'll be fine.

00:22:50.280 --> 00:22:51.560
His lordship must be with the adviser.

00:22:52.470 --> 00:22:54.000
Don't mention her.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:54.880
It's her fault

00:22:54.880 --> 00:22:56.070
that our lord didn't come back at night.

00:22:57.070 --> 00:22:59.400
How can I report to Madam?

00:22:59.400 --> 00:23:00.350
Muskmelon,

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:02.830
are you still thinking about Madam's promise

00:23:02.830 --> 00:23:04.830
that she would let you be his lorship's close maid?

00:23:05.640 --> 00:23:08.680
Not close maid. Concubine. Do you understand?

00:23:09.830 --> 00:23:11.190
How's it better?

00:23:11.830 --> 00:23:13.160
You'll be inferior to others.

00:23:13.640 --> 00:23:14.470
You...

00:23:15.160 --> 00:23:16.190
His lordship is back.

00:23:18.310 --> 00:23:19.590
Where did you go last night, my lord?

00:23:19.590 --> 00:23:20.350
We're worrying about you.

00:23:20.350 --> 00:23:21.350
My lord.

00:23:24.560 --> 00:23:26.000
Thanks to Cong Shun,

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:27.230
I've just come back from the autopsy room.

00:23:34.920 --> 00:23:35.520
What?

00:23:36.350 --> 00:23:36.920
Wash it.

00:23:44.310 --> 00:23:46.280
Adviser, I'll go check the autopsy room.

00:23:53.070 --> 00:23:54.950
Wash it? What a neat freak you are!

00:23:55.520 --> 00:23:57.470
I'm gonna stamp it.

00:23:59.950 --> 00:24:01.070
I won't wash.

00:24:01.800 --> 00:24:05.880
Tang Feilong, you are such a big evil.

00:24:06.110 --> 00:24:08.590
I am an adviser!

00:24:08.590 --> 00:24:10.640
How can I be miserable like this!

00:24:11.190 --> 00:24:13.160
How can I be

00:24:15.760 --> 00:24:16.230
Zucchini,

00:24:16.230 --> 00:24:17.400
bring me some water.

00:24:18.230 --> 00:24:19.160
Adviser.

00:24:19.160 --> 00:24:22.350
The hot water is for my lord to take bath.

00:24:22.680 --> 00:24:24.400
You've already ran back and forth 30 times.

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:27.070
Is he taking a bath or an epilation?

00:24:28.400 --> 00:24:30.000
What a serious neat freak!

00:24:31.470 --> 00:24:32.950
Why so angry, adviser?

00:24:34.070 --> 00:24:35.000
I'm washing clothes.

00:24:35.350 --> 00:24:36.590
Here. Wash mine too.

00:24:36.590 --> 00:24:37.400
Go away.

00:24:40.280 --> 00:24:42.280
Tang has bathed for so long!

00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:44.400
The Qi Family have already arrived.

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:45.280
Really?

00:24:45.280 --> 00:24:45.760
Yep!

00:24:45.760 --> 00:24:46.710
I'll call him.

00:24:46.710 --> 00:24:47.520
What about the clothes?

00:24:48.710 --> 00:24:49.350
You help me to wash it.

00:24:50.070 --> 00:24:50.560
Me?

00:24:54.110 --> 00:24:58.190
Hold court trial.

00:25:01.160 --> 00:25:02.190
Your Honor,

00:25:03.590 --> 00:25:06.560
please help me.

00:25:07.680 --> 00:25:08.230
Landlord Qi,

00:25:08.920 --> 00:25:11.110
when was your daughter missing?

00:25:11.110 --> 00:25:14.560
I remembered to see her

00:25:15.880 --> 00:25:17.680
at night on 8th.

00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:19.680
But in the morning on 9th,

00:25:20.310 --> 00:25:23.560
she went missing.

00:25:24.350 --> 00:25:26.110
It's been seven days form 9th till now.

00:25:26.640 --> 00:25:27.590
Why you report so late?

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:30.880
That's because... That's because I thought

00:25:30.880 --> 00:25:32.590
I thought our lady just ran away from home.

00:25:34.590 --> 00:25:36.680
Why did she run away from home?

00:25:37.400 --> 00:25:39.070
Your Honor, here's the thing,

00:25:41.190 --> 00:25:43.000
I came to an agreement with the Sun Family.

00:25:43.560 --> 00:25:46.520
that my daughter will marry their young master Sun Bufan

00:25:46.520 --> 00:25:49.350
on 15th next month.

00:25:50.350 --> 00:25:51.760
But I never expected that

00:25:53.000 --> 00:25:57.470
it would turn out to be beravement.

00:25:58.160 --> 00:25:58.880
My lord.

00:26:00.350 --> 00:26:01.520
In this case, officer Zheng,

00:26:02.070 --> 00:26:04.230
summon Sun Bufan in the afternoon.

00:26:04.230 --> 00:26:06.880
Hui, Hui...

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:09.880
Your Honor,

00:26:11.520 --> 00:26:13.640
she was fine back then, why it happened so suddenly?

00:26:15.400 --> 00:26:16.640
Why are you coming here?

00:26:16.640 --> 00:26:18.950
This is County Office. You can't run wild here.

00:26:18.950 --> 00:26:20.230
Go back now!

00:26:20.230 --> 00:26:22.590
Uncle, let me see her, please.

00:26:23.110 --> 00:26:24.520
Let me see her for the last time.

00:26:26.000 --> 00:26:27.710
Is he Sun Bufan?

00:26:27.710 --> 00:26:32.470
My Honor, he's my distantly related nephew.

00:26:33.040 --> 00:26:36.070
My daughter's elder cousin Wei Zitong.

00:26:36.950 --> 00:26:38.280
Your Honor,

00:26:39.590 --> 00:26:41.430
this shameless nephew

00:26:41.430 --> 00:26:43.190
was coveting my daughter.

00:26:44.230 --> 00:26:48.520
He pestered my daughter a lot.

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:50.710
Is there any use to say that?

00:26:50.710 --> 00:26:52.280
Let me see Hui, please.

00:26:52.520 --> 00:26:53.430
You wanna see her?

00:26:54.070 --> 00:26:54.880
Only if

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:57.680
I'm dead.

00:26:57.680 --> 00:27:00.110
My lord.

00:27:01.190 --> 00:27:03.470
Wake up, my lord.

00:27:03.470 --> 00:27:05.950
The cousin seems very sad.

00:27:06.560 --> 00:27:08.470
Is there anything wrong for him to

00:27:08.470 --> 00:27:09.470
see his younger cousin?

00:27:09.470 --> 00:27:10.430
No.

00:27:11.470 --> 00:27:12.070
No way.

00:27:13.160 --> 00:27:15.230
My daughter hasn't married.

00:27:15.230 --> 00:27:17.110
How can she be seen by a man casually?

00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:18.560
Okay.

00:27:19.560 --> 00:27:20.070
Landlord Qi,

00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:20.920
go back and have a rest.

00:27:25.040 --> 00:27:27.880
And this guy, he is involved in this case,

00:27:27.880 --> 00:27:28.920
he will stay to help with investigation.

00:27:32.590 --> 00:27:34.950
Qi Hui must be killed for love.

00:27:35.640 --> 00:27:36.280
How so?

00:27:37.830 --> 00:27:40.000
I used to think that her fiance is from a rich family,

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:40.950
he's a playboy,

00:27:40.950 --> 00:27:43.280
so there must be a lot of girls admiring him.

00:27:43.280 --> 00:27:44.310
Maybe one of them

00:27:44.310 --> 00:27:48.520
hold malice towards Qi Hui and killed her.

00:27:49.710 --> 00:27:51.430
But when I saw Wei Zitong today,

00:27:51.430 --> 00:27:53.040
I found that there is another possibility.

00:27:53.310 --> 00:27:55.710
He killed the person he couldn't get.

00:27:57.310 --> 00:27:57.800
No way.

00:27:58.430 --> 00:27:59.110
Why?

00:27:59.800 --> 00:28:03.040
The Qi Family is rich.

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:04.680
Why did Qi Hui wear so shabby like a wench ?

00:28:07.950 --> 00:28:11.400
Unless she chose to run away herself.

00:28:14.800 --> 00:28:17.040
I see. She ran away from her marriage.

00:28:18.710 --> 00:28:20.590
What do you think of this Wei Zitong's feelings

00:28:20.590 --> 00:28:22.920
towards Qi Hui?

00:28:23.560 --> 00:28:24.640
Based on the scene today,

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:26.160
it's definite true love.

00:28:26.950 --> 00:28:28.350
Landlord Qi doesn't think so.

00:28:28.920 --> 00:28:31.560
One-sided love is also a kind of love.

00:28:32.160 --> 00:28:35.710
Love is the longest emotion in the world.

00:28:41.880 --> 00:28:44.520
Good calligraphy! It must be written by a handsome man.

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:47.830
How do you know?

00:28:49.520 --> 00:28:52.760
See. The signature is Tang Tianyuan.

00:28:58.430 --> 00:28:58.950
My lord,

00:29:00.310 --> 00:29:02.920
didn't you say you don't know Tang Tianyuan?

00:29:04.310 --> 00:29:05.230
How can you have his fan?

00:29:05.760 --> 00:29:08.000
Well, an colleague gave it to me

00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:09.400
before.

00:29:09.400 --> 00:29:12.000
It's a waste.

00:29:12.640 --> 00:29:14.310
Do you know how many people

00:29:14.310 --> 00:29:16.590
want Tang Tianyuan's personal gadget?

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:19.520
There's no bonds between you and him.

00:29:21.070 --> 00:29:22.760
The bond between me and him is...

00:29:32.310 --> 00:29:33.310
It's you?!

00:29:36.310 --> 00:29:36.710
No.

00:29:36.710 --> 00:29:37.470
What?

00:29:39.590 --> 00:29:40.310
My lord,

00:29:41.560 --> 00:29:44.040
the bond between Tang Tianyuan and me

00:29:44.040 --> 00:29:46.040
is like destined.

00:29:47.800 --> 00:29:49.830
Although Tang Tianyuan looks very

00:29:49.830 --> 00:29:50.590
amorous,

00:29:51.230 --> 00:29:54.070
but actually he's a gentleman.

00:29:55.040 --> 00:29:58.070
Listen, human can disguise

00:29:59.000 --> 00:30:02.160
but his handwriting can't.

00:30:03.640 --> 00:30:04.310
You know about this too?

00:30:08.110 --> 00:30:09.230
The best goodness is like water.

00:30:09.230 --> 00:30:10.640
My lord, have some fruits.

00:30:10.640 --> 00:30:11.350
Tang Tianyuan.

00:30:11.350 --> 00:30:13.880
Okay, bring it to my room. I'll eat them later.

00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:14.950
Yes.

00:30:22.110 --> 00:30:23.400
His lordship will eat them later.

00:30:24.830 --> 00:30:25.560
Take it.

00:30:29.760 --> 00:30:32.000
I'll excuse myself. My lord.

00:30:39.680 --> 00:30:40.400
My lord.

00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:40.950
Go on.

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:44.590
Muskmelon had some misunderstanding

00:30:44.590 --> 00:30:45.760
with me before.

00:30:46.350 --> 00:30:49.070
But, in order to make it clear,

00:30:49.070 --> 00:30:52.070
I've already told everything to her.

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:54.230
I told her,

00:30:54.230 --> 00:30:57.400
I, Tan Lingyin, won't be distracted,

00:30:57.760 --> 00:31:00.430
my heart is only for Tang Tianyuan.

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:07.920
Are you okay?

00:31:07.920 --> 00:31:08.760
I'm fine.

00:31:11.160 --> 00:31:11.590
My lord,

00:31:12.520 --> 00:31:15.430
could you give me the fan

00:31:15.430 --> 00:31:17.430
considering my affection towards Tang Tianyuan?

00:31:18.920 --> 00:31:19.430
No way.

00:31:22.310 --> 00:31:24.280
Then could you borrow it to me for some days?

00:31:25.560 --> 00:31:27.680
It's too precious to lend.

00:31:32.040 --> 00:31:32.640
So mean.

00:31:44.560 --> 00:31:45.680
What's wrong? Qingchen.

00:31:47.560 --> 00:31:48.230
Are you okay?

00:31:49.950 --> 00:31:51.400
I heard something

00:31:52.040 --> 00:31:53.710
in the streets today.

00:31:54.400 --> 00:31:55.520
About Qi Hui's death?

00:31:57.520 --> 00:31:58.760
They said you are also responsible

00:31:59.350 --> 00:32:00.680
for her death.

00:32:01.710 --> 00:32:03.400
Since we promoted our new book,

00:32:03.710 --> 00:32:04.310
they all said that

00:32:04.310 --> 00:32:05.430
Qi Hui died because she was misled

00:32:05.430 --> 00:32:06.830
by Miaomiaosheng's story.

00:32:06.830 --> 00:32:08.000
I've explained it for many times.

00:32:08.000 --> 00:32:10.160
They just kept talking. So annoying.

00:32:11.160 --> 00:32:13.830
Did they go to the County Office for you?

00:32:13.830 --> 00:32:16.560
Nope. They don't know I am Miaomiaosheng.

00:32:17.470 --> 00:32:21.000
What's more. A straight foot is not afraid of a crooked shoe.

00:32:21.000 --> 00:32:23.400
This case will be solved one day.

00:32:25.230 --> 00:32:25.710
Eat.

