Before that day coming,

00:32:28.350 --> 00:32:30.280
I'll do some cleaning with Fang and Zhuang.

00:32:30.280 --> 00:32:31.470
And close the bookstore for a few days.

00:32:31.470 --> 00:32:32.560
So that those busybodies

00:32:32.560 --> 00:32:34.310
won't wander around the front door.

00:32:34.830 --> 00:32:35.350
Right.

00:32:35.560 --> 00:32:36.040
Yep.

00:32:36.800 --> 00:32:39.110
What's right? Are you silly?

00:32:39.830 --> 00:32:41.920
He who excuses himself accuses himself.

00:32:41.920 --> 00:32:43.710
We don't need to be afraid if we never do wrong.

00:32:45.710 --> 00:32:48.280
Though we should be friendly to our customers,

00:32:48.280 --> 00:32:49.350
we still need to be tough

00:32:49.830 --> 00:32:50.920
to those trouble makers.

00:32:51.520 --> 00:32:52.830
But isn't this case bothering you?

00:32:53.470 --> 00:32:54.560
Nope.

00:32:55.710 --> 00:32:57.800
As a female adviser,

00:32:57.800 --> 00:32:59.350
I have heard a lot rumors.

00:32:59.950 --> 00:33:01.680
In my opinion, life is full of ups and downs,

00:33:02.590 --> 00:33:04.310
If I can't endure such difficulties,

00:33:05.280 --> 00:33:06.350
how can I make my own living?

00:33:07.830 --> 00:33:08.520
Besides,

00:33:09.680 --> 00:33:11.950
I think Magistrate Tang will find out the murderer.

00:33:12.950 --> 00:33:13.590
I believe in him.

00:33:20.800 --> 00:33:21.310
Your Honor,

00:33:22.040 --> 00:33:24.310
I and my cousin grew up together.

00:33:24.310 --> 00:33:25.520
We're attached to each other.

00:33:25.520 --> 00:33:27.000
She didn't like that Sun Bufan.

00:33:27.000 --> 00:33:27.950
And she didn't agree on this marriage.

00:33:28.560 --> 00:33:30.230
My lord, both sides must present their opinions.

00:33:30.800 --> 00:33:32.920
Why not bring Sun Bufan and Yu Huan together here?

00:33:34.230 --> 00:33:34.760
Okay.

00:33:35.800 --> 00:33:36.560
Come up here.

00:33:43.590 --> 00:33:44.070
Your Honor.

00:33:44.470 --> 00:33:46.590
What were you doing on the day Qi Hui died?

00:33:48.400 --> 00:33:50.110
I had been preparing for the Wedding Banquet

00:33:50.520 --> 00:33:52.110
for nearly half a month.

00:33:52.590 --> 00:33:54.000
I was tired out every day.

00:33:54.880 --> 00:33:56.070
So, I went to sleep at about 9 pm.

00:33:56.640 --> 00:33:58.430
It was the same that night.

00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:02.310
But Qi Hui's cousin said,

00:34:02.310 --> 00:34:04.950
they fell in love with each other.

00:34:06.640 --> 00:34:08.800
Yu Huan, you knew your lady well.

00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:09.630
What's your opinion?

00:34:10.600 --> 00:34:13.120
Your Honor, my lady had rarely met Wei Zitong

00:34:13.120 --> 00:34:15.560
in the past ten years.

00:34:15.560 --> 00:34:17.160
How is that possible that they fell in love?

00:34:17.670 --> 00:34:18.520
Liar!

00:34:19.040 --> 00:34:20.949
I grew up with Hui.

00:34:20.949 --> 00:34:22.149
Even we didn't see each other a lot,

00:34:22.710 --> 00:34:25.630
we still wrote to each other frequently, Your Honor.

00:34:27.520 --> 00:34:30.280
If they don't believe what her personal maid said,

00:34:31.870 --> 00:34:33.469
how should they even believe you,

00:34:33.469 --> 00:34:34.629
this opportunist?

00:34:36.040 --> 00:34:38.230
I believe in justice.

00:34:38.230 --> 00:34:39.600
If we can't get justice,

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:41.390
Hui wouldn't rest in peace.

00:34:42.120 --> 00:34:44.630
Hui promised to get married with me.

00:34:44.630 --> 00:34:46.840
How would she fall in love with a despicable man like you!

00:34:47.360 --> 00:34:48.630
Even my family fortunes declined,

00:34:49.280 --> 00:34:50.909
but I read the books of sages,

00:34:50.909 --> 00:34:53.279
and behave as a gentleman, how can I be despicable?

00:34:54.150 --> 00:34:55.560
What did you say?

00:34:55.560 --> 00:34:59.520
It's a hilarious. Your Honor.

00:34:59.520 --> 00:35:04.190
Isn't having an affair despicable? Bah.

00:35:05.000 --> 00:35:06.120
I'm gonna kill you.

00:35:11.190 --> 00:35:11.910
This is County Office.

00:35:11.910 --> 00:35:13.320
My lord. Shall we stop them?

00:35:13.320 --> 00:35:13.760
My lord.

00:35:13.760 --> 00:35:14.760
They won't go too serious.

00:35:15.910 --> 00:35:17.910
Two scholars.

00:35:17.910 --> 00:35:20.080
Their fight is like tickling.

00:35:20.800 --> 00:35:22.470
How could you...

00:35:22.470 --> 00:35:23.000
Go to hell.

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:23.870
I'm gonna kill you.

00:35:25.230 --> 00:35:26.520
Stop!

00:35:26.520 --> 00:35:27.190
Let go.

00:35:28.040 --> 00:35:28.560
Enough!

00:35:28.800 --> 00:35:29.320
So bold.

00:35:29.430 --> 00:35:30.000
Imprudence.

00:35:31.870 --> 00:35:33.190
Stop fighting. Listen to me!

00:35:36.430 --> 00:35:36.910
Your Honor.

00:35:45.950 --> 00:35:48.630
My lord, the folks keep saying that Qi Hui's death

00:35:48.630 --> 00:35:50.470
is related to Miaomiaosheng's novel.

00:35:51.000 --> 00:35:53.000
As a manager in Gutang Bookstore,

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:54.120
our adviser shouldn't take part in this case.

00:35:54.120 --> 00:35:55.150
But after leaving the court,

00:35:55.150 --> 00:35:57.120
she went to ask Wei Zitong in private.

00:35:57.120 --> 00:35:58.080
She's acting suspiciously.

00:35:59.910 --> 00:36:00.430
Adviser,

00:36:00.950 --> 00:36:01.840
is it true?

00:36:02.360 --> 00:36:03.600
I've put up with you for a long time.

00:36:04.230 --> 00:36:06.280
I became the adviser because of my capability.

00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:07.870
Don't suppose I'm inferior to you just because I'm a girl.

00:36:08.390 --> 00:36:09.630
Stop blaming me for everything.

00:36:10.360 --> 00:36:11.390
County Office has its own rule.

00:36:11.950 --> 00:36:13.230
I'm just following the rule.

00:36:14.710 --> 00:36:17.150
Adviser Tan, I'll deduct your salary for one month.

00:36:17.150 --> 00:36:18.560
For what?

00:36:18.560 --> 00:36:19.710
Wise move.

00:36:22.040 --> 00:36:23.230
It's all your fault.

00:36:24.870 --> 00:36:26.230
I'm here for making money.

00:36:28.630 --> 00:36:29.710
All people say Qi Hui's death

00:36:29.710 --> 00:36:30.910
is related to Miaomiaosheng.

00:36:30.910 --> 00:36:32.430
But they never really care about Qi Hui.

00:36:32.430 --> 00:36:33.800
She wore shabby clothes

00:36:33.800 --> 00:36:35.600
and died alone in the mountain.

00:36:36.950 --> 00:36:38.630
And she was choked to death.

00:36:39.630 --> 00:36:41.760
But this is exact the same as in your novel.

00:36:46.040 --> 00:36:47.840
That is my first draft before I came to County Office.

00:36:48.560 --> 00:36:49.520
It's not finalized.

00:36:50.230 --> 00:36:51.230
So where's the draft now?

00:36:51.630 --> 00:36:52.520
Has anyone else seen it?

00:36:55.910 --> 00:36:57.800
Oops. It's still in the study of County Office.

00:37:21.360 --> 00:37:23.230
On a dark and windy night,

00:37:23.630 --> 00:37:25.280
the chilly wind keeps blowing,

00:37:25.950 --> 00:37:27.520
Ms. Gao gets very frightened.

00:37:28.600 --> 00:37:30.320
But for the one she loves,

00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:33.080
she chose to attend the date regardless of danger.

00:37:35.710 --> 00:37:38.080
But Mr. Miao is not here.

00:37:38.080 --> 00:37:39.320
I'm the manager.

00:37:39.320 --> 00:37:40.600
Why are you looking for him?

00:37:42.150 --> 00:37:43.390
Mr. Miao must get inspired

00:37:43.390 --> 00:37:45.320
after hearing his stories.

00:38:00.430 --> 00:38:02.760
Our traveler Miaomiaosheng!
